oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Carroll Baker - CMA International Show
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of Carroll Baker at the CMA International Show. The recording is from an unidentified date. The tape features Baker performing various tracks including: "Ten Little Fingers", "All Them Irons in the Fire", "Cryin' Places", "Little Boy Blue", "The Need In Me", "I'd Go Through It All Again", "Maybe (I'll Get Over You Someday)", and "God's Gift To Me."
